When my best friend was fourteen she began her affair with her 18-year-old foster brother. He told her he &quot;loved her&quot; she bought it.  Two and a half years later she became pregnant and finally told her mother about her affair. It was something I had known about all along , but I didn't tell        anyone because I felt it would betray her trust. I wish I        had . When she first told me of her pregnancy she was so happy. The two of them had talked about having a child . He promised he would marry her if she ever got pregnant. I watched in horror as her dream turned into a horrible nightmare. From all sides she was pushed into having an abortion she didn't want. If you know some one who is sexually active and not using any protection please tell some one who can get them the protection they need. If you really love that person this is the only option. Don't make the same mistake I did.<br>

